dct_title_s: E-Z guide map of New York City
dct_alternative_sm: E-Z guide map of New York City : with patent indicator, showing at a glance the exact location of places of interest, railroad terminals, steamship piers, department stores and street locations / [Prepared for] The Biltmore Hotel.
dct_description_sm: 1 map : col. ; on sheet 31 x 24 cm, folded to 24 x 11 cm
Printed on cardboard; rotating pointer riveted in center.
Includes index to railroad terminals and steamship piers.
Ill. and indexes to streets, points of interest and department stores on verso.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
